  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single Player Bullet Hell, set in a steampunk world.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Rosalyn Escape the hordes of robots and kill her way to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Powers Everything</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rather than ammo, all your guns and gadgets are powered by steam pressure, which must be recharged at vents around the city. Constructs are also powered by steam pressure and have to recharge their steam with the same vents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras/0b06d5f02ce6fffcbb02e65caf175dd5.avif?t=1760297437\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras_big/0b06d5f02ce6fffcbb02e65caf175dd5.avif?t=1760297437 width=1560 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill or be killed</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Self sabotaging robots explode near you to kill you. Can you destroy them before they get you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras/42e5968285ce1335be528634237441ca.avif?t=1760297437\" width=1318 height=1116 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Award Nominations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nominated for best upcoming game in the IMIRT Irish Game Awards in 2025, you play as Rosalyn, a construction worker and must blast her way to survival and make it back to your family and get out of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras/19f23b36bc127c532f65c307372e505c.avif?t=1760297437\" width=600 height=396 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single Player Bullet Hell, set in a steampunk world.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Rosalyn Escape the hordes of robots and kill her way to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Powers Everything</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rather than ammo, all your guns and gadgets are powered by steam pressure, which must be recharged at vents around the city. Constructs are also powered by steam pressure and have to recharge their steam with the same vents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras/0b06d5f02ce6fffcbb02e65caf175dd5.avif?t=1760297437\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras_big/0b06d5f02ce6fffcbb02e65caf175dd5.avif?t=1760297437 width=1560 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill or be killed</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Self sabotaging robots explode near you to kill you. Can you destroy them before they get you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras/42e5968285ce1335be528634237441ca.avif?t=1760297437\" width=1318 height=1116 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Award Nominations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nominated for best upcoming game in the IMIRT Irish Game Awards in 2025, you play as Rosalyn, a construction worker and must blast her way to survival and make it back to your family and get out of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364220/extras/19f23b36bc127c532f65c307372e505c.avif?t=1760297437\" width=600 height=396 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
